                            <i class="fas fa-university"></i>
                            <div>
                                <strong>Bank Transfer</strong>
                                <p>3-5 business days to process, 5-10 days for funds to appear</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="host-cancellations">
                <h2>What Happens If a Host Cancels</h2>
                <p>While rare, host cancellations can occur. When they do, we work quickly to minimize disruption:</p>

